Table.Name: Command
Table.Command:
DECLARE @ActivityNumber INTEGER SET @ActivityNumber = {?DocKey@}
SELECT T0.ClgCode AS 'ActivityNo', T0.Action AS 'Activity', T0.Priority, T1.U_NAME AS 'HandledBy', T2.Name AS 'Type', T3.Name AS 'Subject', T0.Details, T0.personal, T0.Recontact AS 'StartDate', T0.BeginTime AS 'StartTime', T0.endDate AS 'EndDate', T0.ENDTime AS 'EndTime', T0.Duration, T0.DurType, T4.Name AS 'Location', T0.street AS 'AddressStreet', T0.city AS 'AddressCity', T0.room AS 'AddressRoom', T0.state AS 'AddressState', T0.country AS 'AddressCountry', T0.CardCode, T5.CardName, T6.Name AS 'ContactPerson', T0.Tel, T0.Notes, T0.DocType AS 'LinkedDocumentType', T0.DocNum AS 'LinkedDocumentNum', T0.parentType AS 'SourceDocumentType', T0.parentId AS 'SourceDocumentNum', T0.prevActvty, T0.status, T7.name AS 'TaskStatusName' FROM OCLG T0 JOIN OUSR T1 ON T0.AttendUser = T1.INTERNAL_K JOIN OCLT T2 ON T0.CntctType = T2.Code LEFT JOIN OCLS T3 ON T0.CntctSbjct = T3.Code AND T2.Code = T3.Type LEFT JOIN OCLO T4 ON T0.Location = T4.Code JOIN OCRD T5 ON T0.CardCode = T5.CardCode LEFT JOIN OCPR T6 ON T0.CntctCode = T6.CntctCode LEFT JOIN OCLA T7 ON T0.status = T7.statusID WHERE T0.ClgCode = @ActivityNumber

FormulaFieldDefinitions.FormulaFieldDefinition: switch ( {Data.DurType} = 'M' , ToText({Data.Duration}, '#')+' '+{@Title_Minutes}, {Data.DurType} = 'H' , ToText({Data.Duration}, '#')+' '+{@Title_Hours}, {Data.DurType} = 'D' , ToText({Data.Duration}, '#')+' '+{@Title_Days}, TRUE , ToText({Data.Duration}, '#')+' '+{Data.DurType} )
